# Backlog-Planner Override
#
# This file customizes the Backlog-Planner agent for your project.
# Place it at: project/.opencode-overrides/agents/backlog-planner.override.md
#
# The framework agent reads this file at session start and applies its contents.

## Vocabulary

Use these terms consistently in all backlog items, specs, and conversations:

| Term | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| learner | A person taking a course |
| publisher | A person creating course content |
| course | A structured learning experience |
| exercise | An interactive practice activity |
| lesson | A single learning unit within a module |
| module | A group of related lessons |

<!-- Add or modify terms to match your domain. -->

